latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Go little bestie 👯‍♀️

Enjoy ~kid friendly~ juices that are not only nutrient-dense, but “the most delicious juices to ever exist!” 

Hey, we didn’t say it 😉

Our next flavor drop is summer in a bottle ✨🌱We’re excited to announce that we’ve partnered with our friends over at @helpcurehd to create our first Wellness Line, blended with key vitamins and trending functional ingredients, to aid in Men and Women’s Wellness (targeting reproductive health)!
 
HelpCureHD, founded by TNT Reporter, @allie.laforce and MLB Pitcher, @thethree8, is an impact-driven non-profit committed to educating consumers on Huntington’s Disease, a hereditary brain disorder, and its effect on traditional family planning. 10% of each of our partnership blends sold will go directly toward the emotional, financial, and mental support of families aiming to eradicate Huntington’s Disease from their family line.
 
Want to be the first to get this mystery flavor in your hands? Head to our link in bio and subscribe to our newsletter 🍉 Can you guess what it is? 👇

🌱100% PLANT BASED RESIN BOTTLE🌱

We’re excited to let you all in on a little secret we’ve been keeping 🤫 and what better day to announce it than #EarthDay! 

This ground-breaking innovation is the first step toward our goal of increased and on-going sustainability improvements and decreasing our carbon footprint. Barring its label and lid Just Made® Organic Lemonades will now exclusively use materials from plant-based sources removing 30% of petroleum-based content from the bottle, therefore reducing the use of virgin oil-based PET company-wide.  The label is made from Avery Dennison’s Clean Flake™ technology which dissolves in the recycling stream, eliminating the need to remove the label prior to recycling.  

To date, the maximum plant-based content in commercial PET bottles has been 30% from monoethylene glycol (MEG), derived from plant sugar. The new 100% plant-based resin is the first to survive High Pressure Processing or Cold-Pressure Processing, transforming the cold pressed beverage industry and raising the bar for other cold-pressed juice companies.

All those fancy words mean… we did it!! Thank you for helping us help the planet 1 bottle at a time 😉🌱🌎

What do you get when you mix the tropics with functional, whole body wellness?

An unbeetable pear!! (And Just Made, of course 😉)

Which tropical or functional ingredients do you wish we started using? Let us know and we MIGHT just craft a juice for YOU! 👀🌱

What started as a passion for bringing the secrets of the tropics to the US, has grown into a brand dedicated to making a difference both in your family’s life as well as the farming families we work with! 

Our purpose is to bring you the highest quality juices, made with real fruits, veggies, and functional ingredients while also being JUST with the farmers that grow our ingredients for us. To us, that looks like donating 5¢ to their communities schools for every bottle sold. 

Thank you for believing in us and sharing our juice and this journey with us!

Berry Happy Holidays from the Just Made family 💜

The countdown til Christmas has officially begun! ❄️🎄

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Celebrating our farmers today on #NationalFarmersDay and everyday! 🌱

A lot of times the farmers work the hardest, but they receive the least amount in the food value chain. They're trying to create the best possible future for their kids, and at Just Made, we believe they should be given what they deserve and more.

Just Made is about being just with our farmers and guaranteeing a fair price for them.

Our co-founders knew that when they started Just Made, they wanted it to be bigger than themselves. They wanted to give back to the communities they were sourcing from. Because of your support, we're able to do this by giving back 5¢ for every bottle that we sell to the farming communities by supporting education for our farming families.

From new bathrooms to new computers, each bottle that you've purchased from Just Made or your local grocery store is directly impacting the farming families we work with. From our farmers to you, let's continue working together to make a difference in this world! Just Made. Made Justly.®

✨To learn more about our farmers and our give back program, click the link in our bio!✨

Let’s Talk About Sugar – The Truth You Should Know 
Not all sugar is created equal — and at Just Made, we believe in keeping it real (and naturally sweet).

Here’s the scoop:
* Added Sugars – Refined sweeteners added during processing. These provide empty calories and can lead to spikes in blood sugar.
*Natural Sugars – Found in whole fruits and veggies, these come with fiber, vitamins, and antioxidants that support overall wellness.

Just Made juices have zero added sugars — only the natural sweetness from fresh-pressed fruits and vegetables. So you can sip confidently, knowing you’re nourishing your body without the junk.

Taste the difference. Feel the difference.

Tenderize & Energize with Pineapple Ginger Juice 🍍🔥
Fire up the grill—your secret weapon just came out of the cooler.

Why it Works
Our Pineapple Ginger cold-pressed juice is loaded with fresh pineapple  to break down tough muscle fibers, plus zingy ginger, bright lime, and naturally hydrating coconut water for a juicy, flavor-packed finish.

Quick Marinade How-To

Pour: Combine 1 cup Pineapple Ginger juice with 2 Tbsp soy sauce, 1 Tbsp olive oil, and a pinch of chili flakes.

Soak: Coat flank steak, pork shoulder, or chicken thighs. Chill 30–60 min—no mushy meat!

Grill: Pat dry, season, and sear over high heat for a caramelized crust and melt-in-your-mouth bite.

Serve: Slice, squeeze fresh lime, and bask in the sweet-savory glory.

💡 Pro Tip: Skip canned pineapple—heat kills natural nutrients. Use fresh instead.
